  <p>
    The point of <em>LifeLoggerz</em> isn’t just to show what I track — it’s to show <strong>why</strong> I started doing it in the first place.
    Here are the people, projects, and philosophies that pushed me down this rabbit hole of data and discipline.
  </p>

  {/* 1. Phil Von Stade */}
  <SectionHero
    src="/images/phil_von_stade.png"
    alt="Phil Von Stade life-logging video thumbnail"
